

📘 Spring Boot Roadmap — Beginner to Advanced
This roadmap gives you a clear, structured path to learn Spring Boot from zero to job‑ready backend developer.
It includes the core concepts, learning order, and visual diagrams to make everything stick.

🧭 1. Overview — What Is Spring Boot?
Spring Boot is a framework that makes it easy to build production‑ready Java applications by providing:

Starters

Auto‑Configuration

Embedded servers (Tomcat)

Production‑ready features (Actuator)

Minimal configuration

